# TypeScript and Node.js Standards

- Follow TypeScript best practices with proper typing
- Use async/await patterns consistently  
- Implement proper error handling with try/catch blocks
- Follow Node.js and AWS Lambda best practices
- Use appropriate logging levels and structured logging
- Ensure proper resource cleanup and memory management
- Always build and test locally after making changes
- Add tests to cover new functionality
- Document significant changes in docs/
